<h2>What are the navigation lights allowed for a vessel under oars?</h2>

<<set $questionOption = [
    "Electric torch or lantern",
    "Electric torch and white sidelights", 
    "White bow light and white stern light", 
    "Electric torch only"
]>>
<<questionMacro "Its navigation lights are:" $questionOption "Electric torch or lantern">>

<div class="incorrectFeedback hidden">
    <h3>Not quite. </h3>
    <p>Vessels under oars (electric torch/lantern showing white light, or may use same lights as sailing vessels). That said, we recommend bow and stern lights at least.</p>
</div>

